HEADWORD: Tapper
<hw>Tap"per</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The
lesser spotted woodpecker (<spn>Dendrocopus minor</spn>); -- called also
<altname>tapperer</altname>, <altname>tabberer</altname>,
<altname>little wood pie</altname>, <altname>barred
woodpecker</altname>, <altname>wood tapper</altname>,
<altname>hickwall</altname>, and <altname>pump borer</altname>.</def>
